  "worldId": "block",
  "title": "矿洞火把路：寻找亮处",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "mine",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/block/block-02.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "矿洞里黑黑的，墙上只有一串忽明忽暗的火把。守门人说，光亮会带来安全。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是矿洞火把路。我们先把“寻找亮处”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到方块碰撞的声音，新的建造点就在前面。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先找稳固的方块，再一步一步搭出安全的路线。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "scan",
          "prompt": "找出矿洞里下一盏亮着的火把。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "点亮左边火把",
              "feedback": "火光照见了安全的石阶。"
            },
            {
              "label": "观察墙上星点",
              "feedback": "星点组成箭头，指向前方。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，点亮左边火把让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "方块放稳后，藏在墙后的通道露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这段通道接到村子的道路上，伙伴们就能一起通过。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这块特别的方块，它会成为下一座建筑的起点。",
          "character": "block_builder",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "‘明’和‘亮’都能让我们看清前面的路。",
          "character": "cave_keeper",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
        "characters": [
          "narrator",
          "cave_keeper",
          "hero"
        ],
